          <div class="pi-item"><svg class="pi-ic" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 3c.132 0 .263 0 .393 0a7.5 7.5 0 0 0 7.92 12.446a9 9 0 1 1 -8.313 -12.454z"/><path d="M17 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2a2 2 0 0 0 -2 2a2 2 0 0 0 -2 -2a2 2 0 0 0 2 -2"/></svg><div><div class="pi-t">Memorable moments</div><div class="pi-d">A moment they didn't expect</div></div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="tier-lbl">Going further <span class="tl-line"></span></div>
        <div class="tier-sub">The difference between good and unforgettable.</div>
        <div class="pillars-intro further">
          <div class="pi-item further-item"><svg class="pi-ic" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M8 13v-8.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 0v7.5"/><path d="M11 11.5v-2a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 0v2.5"/><path d="M14 10.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 0v1.5"/><path d="M17 11.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 0v4.5a6 6 0 0 1 -6 6h-2h.208a6 6 0 0 1 -5.012 -2.7l-.196 -.3c-.312 -.479 -1.407 -2.388 -3.286 -5.728a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 .536 -2.022a1.867 1.867 0 0 1 2.28 .28l1.47 1.47"/></svg><div><div class="pi-t">Active participation</div><div class="pi-d">Guests do, not just watch</div></div></div>
