        <p class="eyebrow">Step 1 of 3 · Tell</p>
        <h2 class="h1">Three questions to start.</h2>
        <p class="lede" style="margin-bottom:20px;">Your answers shape the arc, the peak, and the listing.</p>

        <div class="pq-wrap">

          <!-- Q1 -->
